name: Experiment Or Die #36
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. Only a month into this project and I'm already finding time management to be tricky because I work full time as a graphic designer and I have a wife and a 3.5 year old daughter. They are unquestionably by inspiration and muses so they drive me to create, but the time needed to create takes me away from them. A dilemma any person who has a passion for something must deal with. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
